HellDAO’s referral system is designed to drive growth and reward users who promote the platform. By staking $HELL tokens, users can generate unique referral links. When new participants join through these links and earn rewards, the referrer receives 5% of their earnings.

--------------------------

Ecosystem Growth: Each referral strengthens the protocol as new users stake their tokens, increasing the overall stability.

Treasury Expansion: New users contribute to the treasury, supporting HellDAO’s investments and liquidity management.

Incentives for Promotion: Users who actively promote the protocol are rewarded, aligning community and protocol goals for long-term success.
